<title>USA: Illinova authorizes 4 mln share repurchase.</title>
<headline>Illinova authorizes 4 mln share repurchase.</headline>
<dateline>DECATUR, Ill. 1997-06-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Illinova Corp said Tuesday its board of directors authorized the repurchase of up to four million shares of the company's common stock.</p>
<p>The shares would be acquired in the open market, private negotiations and other transactions.</p>
<p>Shares of Illinova, a utility holding company, closed up 1/4 at 20-1/2.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
